
# Gem2deb

## Gem2deb requires adaption in order to install the ruby gems into the correct folder

Adaptions are maintained at https://github.com/2maz/gem2deb for various platforms

## The original sources can be found at

 * https://anonscm.debian.org/cgit/pkg-ruby-extras/gem2deb.git
 * https://salsa.debian.org/ruby-team/gem2deb

## Generate updated version for new distribution

 * rebase the existing changes on the particular version you need
 * build the version and add the deb files to the repository
  * DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS=nocheck dpkg-buildpackage -d -a i386 -uc -us
